{"tid":1647144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點先維持嗌「五大訴求」？","createTime":"2019-10-11T15:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T02:41:13.000Z","uid":241093,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5c20a587f06dceb18573df9b40342d3a0a0b2145","tid":1647144,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:30:07.000Z","msg":"頭先德福唱國歌 <br />\n無啦啦嗌六大訴求缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻呆咗 身邊班人冇再和應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以一致嗌返五大訴求？<br />\n訴求係無限嘅，<br />\n但五大入面有真普選係終極大佬就夠皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">嗌六大訴求其實係咪想分散聲音<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n同埋好多人都混淆第六大訴求究竟係乜<br />\n遲啲又立其他惡法唔通又七大、八大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n維持五大訴求，<br />\n額外訴求額外口號！</span></span>"},{"pid":"e636746db69d1a097d146a079c69c4edef8d0f95","tid":1647144,"uid":241093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:31:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n全民口罩，瓦解惡法！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c691dc275369cc37c5c4557f561f7d58f56f624f","tid":1647144,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:37:49.000Z","msg":"係五大訴求啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋一致嗌口號好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a60ab4b1553a8fcce4ab107a0db3de319ef5a21","tid":1647144,"uid":290407,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:38:23.000Z","msg":"解散警隊，係成立獨立調查委員會既家強版訴求<br />\n同意唔好叫六大訴求，攤開手掌五隻手指，五大訴求，咁先有sound bite."},{"pid":"b0aeaca2bb71b8c5fcc359e2a4e6c2e5a0abe40f","tid":1647144,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:41:11.000Z","msg":"六大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"04d1e4ec034254a55eb795268a93a5262bac3f2e","tid":1647144,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0aeaca2bb71b8c5fcc359e2a4e6c2e5a0abe40f","tid":1647144,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:41:11.000Z","msg":"六大訴求 缺一不可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:44:38.000Z","msg":"一致口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求！"},{"pid":"5cd51c9b53d1eaa9155458fef3de609a21c4ff7b","tid":1647144,"uid":217441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:55:03.000Z","msg":"五大訴求呀"},{"pid":"7801a5b4ddf672379f631dab87b2fa6cc8124209","tid":1647144,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:55:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e45678cd02929bf6b5207c4a55de5d4cd4916b8","tid":1647144,"uid":275009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a60ab4b1553a8fcce4ab107a0db3de319ef5a21","tid":1647144,"uid":290407,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T15:38:23.000Z","msg":"解散警隊，係成立獨立調查委員會既家強版訴求<br />\n同意唔好叫六大訴求，攤開手掌五隻手指，五大訴求，咁先有sound bite."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:57:31.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n解散警隊唔知點實行，不如叫改組仲好 <br />\n但無論點 獨立調查委員會 都係最重要"},{"pid":"91c5b2bb2721afe8765af0a6b7fdd87314d53ee2","tid":1647144,"uid":217441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T14:00:12.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n係五大訴求呀！<br />\n<br />\n